'''Attack Attack!'''是一個美國[[金屬核|金屬核]]樂團。他們來自[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]。目前屬於[[Rise唱片|Rise唱片]]旗下的樂團。自2005年成立以來，他們發行過一張EP《If Guns Are Outlawed, Can We Use Swords?》和兩張專輯，分別是《Someday Came Suddenly》與一張《<nowiki>Attack Attack!</nowiki>》。

雖然樂團有些歌曲，包含[[基督教|基督教]]性的歌詞，成員並不是全都[[基督徒|基督徒]]，他們也自認不是基督教樂團。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hardtimes.ca/attackattack09 |title=Attack Attack "We're not a Christian band" - hardtimes.ca |date=13 July 2009 |accessdate=1 November 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090717235120/http://www.hardtimes.ca/attackattack09 |archivedate=2009年7月17日 }}</ref>

==樂團歷史==
=== 成軍與作品《Someday Came Suddenly》 (2005–2008) ===
成立於2007年間的Attack Attack!，創始團員為Austin Carlile、Ricky Lortz、Andrew Whiting、Nick White與Andrew Wetzel。其後Johnny Franck取代了Ricky Lortz成為新的吉他與歌手、John Holgado則是取代了Nick White成為新的貝斯手。

2008年初，樂團獨立發行了[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]《If Guns Are Outlawed, Can We Use Swords?》，接著在同年六月獲得[[Rise唱片|Rise唱片]]的簽約，並發行第一張專輯《Someday Came Suddenly》。<ref>[http://www.musicemissions.com/artists/albums/index.php?album_id=9795 Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.musicemissions.com/artists/albums/index.php?album_id=9795 |date=20110714134011 }}, MusicEmissions.com</ref>發行之時，作品獲得[[告示牌|告示牌]]200第25位、獨立專輯排行榜第193位。<ref>[{{Allmusic|class=artist|id=p1092680/charts-awards|pure_url=yes}} Charts], [[Allmusic|Allmusic]]</ref>儘管這張作品帶了許多負評，但仍在第一個禮拜賣出了3600張。<ref>[http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1599721/20081119/swift__taylor.jhtml Taylor Swift Scores First #1 Debut with Fearless] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1599721/20081119/swift__taylor.jhtml |date=20101028054409 }}. [[MTV|MTV]], November 19, 2008</ref>

===主唱Carlile的離去與新主唱Barham的來到 (2008–2009)===
在與樂團[[Maylene_and_the_Sons_of_Disaster|Maylene and the Sons of Disaster]]巡迴之時，<ref>[http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/maylene-and-the-sons-of-disaster-a-static-lullaby-showbread-confide-attack-attack/Event?oid=852515&show=comments Attack Attack! Maylene & the Sons of Disaster, A Static Lullaby, Showbread, Confide, Attack Attack!] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/maylene-and-the-sons-of-disaster-a-static-lullaby-showbread-confide-attack-attack/Event?oid=852515&show=comments |date=20121015182815 }} [[Chicago_Reader|Chicago Reader]]</ref>主唱[[Austin_Carlile|Austin Carlile]]忽然辭退主唱一職，離開樂團，換上For All We Know的前主唱Nick Barham。

2009年，他們為[[Fearless唱片|Fearless唱片]]錄製《[[Punk_Goes...|Punk Goes...]]》系列第八張專輯《[[Punk_Goes_Pop_2|Punk Goes Pop 2]]》，Attack Attack!翻唱了[[Katy_Perry|Katy Perry]]的"[[I_Kissed_a_Girl|I Kissed a Girl]]"，這是前主唱Austin Carlile離開前就錄製好的。接著他們展開巡迴，與樂團[[Escape_the_Fate|Escape the Fate]]、[[William_Control|William Control]]、[[Black_Tide|Black Tide]]和[[Burn_Halo|Burn Halo]]<ref>[http://altpress.com/news/5318.htm Escape the Fate Heading Out with Attack Attack!] {{Wayback|url=http://altpress.com/news/5318.htm |date=20120323012352 }}. ''[[Alternative_Press|Alternative Press]]'', December 9, 2008.</ref>

除此之外，他們參加了2009年的[[Warped巡迴|Warped巡迴]]，與無利益團體Music Saves Lives簽約，與捐血的歌迷們見面。<ref>[http://vanswarpedtour.com/blog/0/6 Music Saves Lives Donation '09 The Dillinger Escape Plan, Attack Attack!] {{Wayback|url=http://vanswarpedtour.com/blog/0/6 |date=20111029055020 }} Warped Tour</ref>

===主唱Barham的離去 (2009–2010)===

Attack Attack!拍攝了他們最具爭議性的歌曲《Stick Stickly》的MV，這支音樂影帶同樣也引發一連串的批評，唱片公司Buddyhead與英國報紙''The Guardian''接大篇幅評論。<ref name="Guardian.co.uk"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.buddyhead.com/crab-core-redo-attack-attack-make-new-stick-stickly-video/ |title=Buddyhead.com |access-date=2011-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101018052521/http://www.buddyhead.com/crab-core-redo-attack-attack-make-new-stick-stickly-video |archive-date=2010-10-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> The band also has a "live" video for the song "Dr. Shavargo Pt. 3".<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.noisecreep.com/2009/08/14/attack-attack-dr-shavargo-pt-3-live-video/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-10-20 |archive-date=2011-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007071439/http://www.noisecreep.com/2009/08/14/attack-attack-dr-shavargo-pt-3-live-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

十月19日，在Attack Attack!主場巡演前兩天，主唱Nick Barham宣布離開樂團，在他的MySpace上說：「這是改變的時候，」而非與團員不合。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=blog.view&friendId=38429436&blogId=515005017 |title=NEWS!!!! - Nick's MySpace Blog {{!}} |accessdate=2011-10-20 |archive-date=2009-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207065936/http://blogs.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=blog.view |dead-url=no }}</ref>這樣臨時的變動，他們只好讓身為鍵盤手的Caleb Shomo擔任主唱。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=blog.view&friendId=35990775&blogId=515397907 |title=Regarding Member Change - ATTACK ATTACK!'s MySpace Blog {{!}}# |accessdate=2011-10-20 |archive-date=2009-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028235433/http://blogs.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=blog.view&friendId=35990775&blogId=515397907 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

年底之時，Attack Attack!還與樂團[[I_Set_My_Friends_On_Fire|I Set My Friends On Fire]]、[[Miss_May_I|Miss May I]]、[[Our_Last_Night|Our Last Night]]與[[The_Color_Morale|The Color Morale]]展開 ''Shred Til You're Dead''巡迴。在這場巡迴中，他們首次公開來自新專輯《<nowiki>Attack Attack!</nowiki>》的曲目《Sexual Man Chocolate》。

===同名專輯與Franck的離去 (2010–2011)===
2010年，Attack Attack!成為《Artery Across the Nation巡迴》的主秀，與樂團[[Asking_Alexandria|Asking Alexandria]]、[[I_See_Stars|I See Stars]]、[[Breathe_Carolina|Breathe Carolina]]與[[Bury_Tomorrow|Bury Tomorrow]]在年初同台演出。在發片前夕，他們更進一步演奏了三首來自《<nowiki>Attack Attack!</nowiki>》的歌曲。分別是《Sexual Man Chocolate》、《AC-130》和《A For Andrew》。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5c3sBZP3tSw |title=Attack Attack! (Andrew W.) *interview w/ Punk World Views* |publisher=Punk World Views/[[YouTube|YouTube]] |date=28 November 2009 |accessdate=12 January 2010 |archive-date=2013-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724152642/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5c3sBZP3tSw |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年六月8日發行了同名專輯。

樂團在[[Warped巡演|Warped巡演]]期間，於Altec Lansing舞台全場演出，同樣也參與十一月的《This Is a Family 巡演》。<ref>[http://eventful.com/grandrapids/events/artery-foundation-across-nation-tour-ft-attack-/E0-001-027294875-5 Artery Foundation Across The Nation Tour ft Attack Attack!] {{Wayback|url=http://eventful.com/grandrapids/events/artery-foundation-across-nation-tour-ft-attack-/E0-001-027294875-5 |date=20100324214743 }} Eventful</ref>

十一月10日，Johnny Franck也決定離開樂團，他希望能夠藉由音樂，建立與神的關係，另外組了樂團[[The_March_Ahead|The March Ahead]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theprp.com/2010/11/11/news/attack-attack-guitarist-johnny-franck-leaves-band-to-refocus-on-god |title=/Attack Attack! guitarist/vocalist Johnny Franck leaves band to “Refocus on God” |accessdate=2011-10-20 |archive-date=2012-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218002915/http://www.theprp.com/2010/11/11/news/attack-attack-guitarist-johnny-franck-leaves-band-to-refocus-on-god/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.metalsucks.net/2010/11/12/oh-noes-attack-attack-loses-another-member/#comments OH NOES ATTACK ATTACK LOSES ANOTHER MEMBER] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metalsucks.net/2010/11/12/oh-noes-attack-attack-loses-another-member/#comments |date=20120116072831 }} MetalSucks</ref>因此，樂團放送了一首由Caleb Shomo包辦清腔與吼腔的歌曲。<ref>[http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/attack_attack_guitarist_vocalist_johnny_franck_leaves_band_to_refocus_on_go/  Attack Attack! guitarist/vocalist Johnny Franck leaves band to “refocus on God”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/attack_attack_guitarist_vocalist_johnny_franck_leaves_band_to_refocus_on_go/ |date=20120822074714 }} ''[[Alternative_Press|Alternative Press]]''</ref>來自樂團[[My_Ticket_Home|My Ticket Home]]的主唱Sean Mackowski暫時遞補這個空職。而MV''Smokahontas''在隔年的一月21日發布。<ref>{{cite web|last=Karan|first=Tim|title=Attack Attack! premiere "Smokahontas" video|url=http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/attack_attack_premiere_smokahontas_video/|publisher=[[Alternative_Press|Alternative Press]]|accessdate=30 May 2011|date=21 January 2011|archive-date=2012-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120714051534/http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/attack_attack_premiere_smokahontas_video|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中，My Ticket Home的主唱Sean Mackowski和[[In_Fear_and_Faith|In Fear and Faith]]的前主唱Cody Anderson都參與了MV的拍攝。<ref>{{cite web|title=ATTACK ATTACK Debut New Video For "Smokahontas"|url=http://thenewreview.net/news/attack-attack-debut-new-video-for-%E2%80%9Csmokahontas%E2%80%9D|publisher=The New Review|accessdate=17 June 2011|date=21 January 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110127121836/http://thenewreview.net/news/attack-attack-debut-new-video-for-%E2%80%9Csmokahontas%E2%80%9D|archivedate=2011年1月27日}}</ref>終於在2011年，Attack Attack!在[[Warped_Tour|Warped Tour]]的主場舞台上表演。

樂團開始計畫於七月19日，發行豪華版的同名專輯，增加四首新歌、兩首未插電版與兩首混音版。新歌《Last Breath》先行在七月7日公開宣傳。這也是第一首正式歌曲，由Caleb Shomo負責清腔與吼腔，音樂製作人為John Feldmann。第三張專輯也預計在2012年初發行。<ref>{{cite web|title=Exclusive: Attack Attack! will re-release their self-titled album with 4 new songs on July 19th!|url=http://grafwall.indiestar.tv/2011/05/attack-attack-will-re-release-their.html?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=facebook&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+indiestarTV+(IndieStar+TV)|publisher=Indiestar|accessdate=1 June 2011|date=31 May 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110817112305/http://grafwall.indiestar.tv/2011/05/attack-attack-will-re-release-their.html?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=facebook&utm_campaign=Feed:+indiestarTV+(IndieStar+TV)|archivedate=2011年8月17日|df=}}</ref>

===第三張專輯《This Means War》(2011–)===
Caleb Shomo在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上表示，他們的第三張專輯《This Means War》已經錄製完成了。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.alterthepress.com/2011/11/attack-attack-complete-work-on-new.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-11-08 |archive-date=2019-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215134039/http://www.alterthepress.com/2011/11/attack-attack-complete-work-on-new.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這張專輯有十個曲目，預計在2012年一月27日發行。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.alterthepress.com/2011/12/attack-attack-reveal-new-album-this.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-12 |archive-date=2012-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120701214249/http://www.alterthepress.com/2011/12/attack-attack-reveal-new-album-this.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>專輯單曲《The Motivation》在十二月12日公開。此外，這張專輯的主場巡演《This Means War巡迴》將與有樂團The Ghost Inside, Sleeping with Sirens, Chunk! No Captain Chunk, and Dream On, Dreamer暖場演出。<ref name=APNA>{{cite web|title=Attack Attack! announce new album, 2012 headlining tour dates|url=http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/attack_attack_announce_new_album_2012_headlining_tour_dates?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter&utm_campaign=altpress|publisher=Alternative Press|accessdate=14 November 2011|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127083326/http://www.altpress.com/news/entry/attack_attack_announce_new_album_2012_headlining_tour_dates?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter&utm_campaign=altpress|dead-url=no}}</ref>而後，MV《The Wretched》於一月12日發布。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jiOepsyiVR8 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-14 |archive-date=2012-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120114065504/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jiOepsyiVR8&gl=US&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>
